title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
